Legend:
    [STICK]: Joystick control; push up: forward/up, etc.
    [HOLD]: Runs while held down
    [CLICK]: Runs after clicked once

Gamepad 1:

Drive:
    [STICK] L/R Joysticks: Field Centric with Mechanum

Intake:
    Intake Rollers:
        Run: [HOLD] Right Trigger
    Intake Slides:
        Base Preset: [CLICK] DPad Down
        Transfer Preset: [CLICK] DPad Right
        Extend Preset: [CLICK] DPad Up
    Intake Tilt:
        Swap Preset: [CLICK] Right Bumper


Gamepad 2:

Outtake:
    Outtake Slides:
        Base Preset: [CLICK] DPad Down
        Transfer Preset: [CLICK] DPad Right
        Extend Preset: [CLICK] DPad Up

        Manual Control: [STICK Y] Left Stick
    Outtake Bucket Tilt:
        Swap Preset: [CLICK] Right Bumper

Intake
    Intake Slides
        Manual Control: [STICK Y] Right Stick










